.TH devin-list 1  "list " 
.SH NAME
devin\-list \- List sessions in the current directory
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdevin list\fR [\fB\-\-format\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
List sessions in the current directory
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-format\fR \fI<FORMAT>\fR [default: interactive]
Output format
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
interactive: Interactive session picker (default)
.IP \(bu 2
json: JSON output
.IP \(bu 2
csv: CSV output
.RE
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
